  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "There is no change in the price of fuel",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official of the Ministry of Energy said that according to the petroleum price formula, there is no change in the price of fuel and the existing price of all types of fuel is still valid.",
        "According to the petroleum price formula, the price revision was scheduled to be implemented yesterday (15) in the middle of August, but it was not a revision, the official further said.",
        "Accordingly, a liter of octane 92 petrol is Rs 450, a liter of octane 95 petrol is Rs 540, a liter of auto diesel is Rs 430 and a liter of super diesel is Rs 510."
      ],
